divs: Sighting DetailsFour red-orange glowing orbs flying over Kranj (Slovenia, Europe) on New years eve beetwen 22.00 and 23.00 CET (GMT +1) followed by another one same in shape, colour and size. Went out on a balcony on the 7th floor when I saw it coming from the NW toward SE. It was flying (moving) in one direction, passed by quite fast.
Summary: Five red-orange glowing orbs flying over Kranj (Slovenia, Europe)
trends: There have been no other sightings in Kranj
